item.title: Portals
item.dc:creator: @si_force Si Force
item.description:
@si_force wrote:

You’d add this code under the correct switch statement:

case ####: teleportToX = xxxx; teleportToY = yyyy; break;

You’d change the ####'s to the portal ID you are using and also the X’s and Y’s to the place where you wish the portal to teleport you to.
